<span class="PRTitle"><!-- NewsTitle.start -->Senator Francis 'Chiz' Escudero's Press Conference<!-- NewsTitle.end --></span>
<br /><span class="PRSub"><!-- NewsTitleSub.start -->FULL TRANSCRIPT <br />
VENUE: Cucina Ni Bunso Restaurant - Quezon City<!-- NewsTitleSub.end--></span>
</p>
